ARC TASK 35ab12c3
spatial reasoning puzzle 35ab12c3
the sea perceives training pairs then applies the rule to the test input

observe spatial_eye.rana
observe arc2_spatial_eye.rana

@filter task_colors
  "black"  "blue"  "red"  "green"  "yellow"  "magenta"  "orange"  "cyan"

PERCEPTION arc_task_35ab12c3
energy 0.50
phase 0.00
spin 0.50
coherence 0.90
coupling 0.50

COGNITION arc_training_count_3
energy 0.45
phase 0.00
spin 0.50
coherence 0.80

@perceive task_summary
DETECT task_id: 35ab12c3
DETECT training_pairs: 3
DETECT test_inputs: 1

